name: Mr Eggo +Stylizara / Painted eggs
description:
It was an interesting idea to combine several models. I combined the theme of painting eggs and paint that I had already created earlier (Stylizara model). I called this model Mr. Ego, it turned out bright and unusual combinations. Of course, almost this could be done with a regular supplement, but here I have selected different models with faces on eggs. Therefore, you need to add the model Mr. Ego and Stylezara Stylezara as well as add the necessary descriptions and you will definitely have interesting painted in paint, and maybe not only, eggs.

  • Mr Eggo + Stylizara = ✨✨

  • Base model, Trained on - cineDiffusion #cinediffusion

  • Steps 4 000

  • <hypernet:MrEggo:0.7> cute ((cartoon painted smiling egg))

  • example: <hypernet:MrEggo:0.7> cute ((cartoon painted smiling egg)) <hypernet:Stylizara-3900:0.7>

  • ( ~ From 4 to 9 )

  • Each checkpoint has its own charms, where it's better, where it's terrible, that's why the result "generation" is always not what you want right away.

  • Please leave feedback and images you manage to create with ❤

  • I'm just trying, so don't judge strictly, I hope you like it
